    try {
        cosStorageService.moveFile(outgoingKey, failedKey);
        log.info("Moved retry file back to failed location: {} -> {}", outgoingKey, failedKey);
    } catch (Exception moveEx) {
        log.error("Failed to move retry file back to failed location: {} -> {}", outgoingKey, failedKey, moveEx);
    }
}
```

That version is also fine if your `moveFile` already handles missing source cleanly.

